Main requirements

1.  Read config file
2.  Write config file
     -- another module since slaves have same
3.  Get replication slots
4.  create replication slots
    -- easy enough
5.  Determine if changes need to be written
6.  determine if restart is needed
7.  issue reload and restart operations

5-7 are built on a basic state machine.
1.  Config changes to be changed
